text: Meaden is the surname of: * Deborah Meaden (born 1959), English businesswoman * Henry Meaden (1862–?), English cricketer * John Meaden, Bishop of Newfoundland 1956–1965 * Levi Meaden (born c.1987), Canadian actor * Peter Meaden (1941–1978), music publicist, managed the Who * Terence Meaden (born 1935), British archaeologist
title: Meaden
